<article id="post-617" class="post-617 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general category-technology tag-content-management">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/02/reddot-keynote-at-summit-2007/" rel="bookmark">RedDot Keynote at Summit 2007</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Okay, hard for me to avoid it now. We use RedDot. There, I&#8217;ve said it. Now let&#8217;s move on.<br />
Met Detlef Kamps (RedDot President) last night. Nice guy. German, and speaks English very well. Looking forward to my breakfast meeting with him on Wednesday. Looked more comfortable last night. Must be the suit.<br />
Going around the room, pointing out key RedDot people. Met most of them already. Handy to put faces to names.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/02/reddot-keynote-at-summit-2007/#more-617" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;RedDot Keynote at Summit 2007&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/02/reddot-keynote-at-summit-2007/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2007-02-12T11:26:38-07:00">12 February 2007</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/technology/" rel="category tag">Technology</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/content-management/" rel="tag">content management</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/02/reddot-keynote-at-summit-2007/#respond">Leave a comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on RedDot Keynote at Summit 2007</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
