<article id="post-613" class="post-613 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-careers category-general tag-critical-mass">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/01/new-rolex-website-live/" rel="bookmark">The new Rolex website is live</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><!-- ckey="5B4B9317" -->Over a year ago, we started on a brave new project: bring a whole new experience to the Rolex brand.<br />
It&#8217;s been a tough year. Countless designs. Several prototypes. A lot of lost sleep. (Not to mention some martial discord as a result of working too much.)<br />
I offer you the <a href="http://www.rolex.com/en/">brand new and improved Rolex.com website</a>.<br />
