	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2007/01/funeral-for-dale-garraway/" rel="bookmark">Funeral for Dale Garraway</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>On Tuesday, 2 January, Dale Garraway passed away at the age of 57. His funeral was today, attended by several hundred friends and family.<br />
I didn&#8217;t know Dale all that well &#8212; he was still Mr. Garraway to me &#8212; but I&#8217;m close friends with his daughter, Tamara. She&#8217;d been my housemate for over two years and we&#8217;ve known each other for about six and a half years. We&#8217;ve seen each other through quite a bit.<br />
